[SHORT DESC]
10% chance to freeze the target.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage and has a 10% chance to freeze the target.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Ice Punch is an accurate and reliable Ice-type move, its only problem is that it's Special and Ice Beam and Blizzard exist. Only use it in tradebacks when neither of these options are available.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rb/moves/ice_beam">Ice Beam</a> is a more powerful option that has a chance to freeze the target.</p>
<p><a href="/rb/moves/blizzard">Blizzard</a> is a more powerful option that has a chance to freeze the target.</p>